查佩尔·罗恩（Chappell Roan https://www.nme.com/news/music/chappell-roan-achieves-first-first-number-one-number-one-single-with-pink-pony-club-pony-club-five-five-five-five-five five-fter-its-its-intial-initial-initial-initial-initial-initial-initial-intial-intial-initial-intial-intial-reas-3844687?u tm_source = rss＆utm_medium = rss＆utm_campaign = chappell-roan-acchieves-first-uk-number-number-number-single-with-with-pink-ponk-pony-club-pony-club五年 - 五年徒气 -  itter-its-its-its intitial-initial-initial-intial-releaseLaura Molloy Sat, 08 Mar 2025 11:50:37 +0000 Music NewsNewsPop https://www.nme.com/?p=3844687 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Chappell-Roan.-CREDIT_-Jeff-Kravitz_FilmMagic.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" fetchpriority="high" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Chappell-Roan.-CREDIT_-Jeff-Kravitz_FilmMagic.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Chappell-Roan.-CREDIT_-Jeff-Kravitz_FilmMagic-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Chappell-Roan.-CREDIT_-Jeff-Kravitz_FilmMagic-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Chappell-Roan.-CREDIT_-Jeff-Kravitz_FilmMagic-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Chappell-Roan.-CREDIT_-Jeff-Kravitz_FilmMagic-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Chappell-Roan.-CREDIT_-Jeff-Kravitz_FilmMagic-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>这首歌于2020年首次通过大西洋唱片发行，然后罗恩（Roan）后来从唱片公司删除</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/chappell-roan-achieves-first-uk-number-one-single-with-pink-pony-club-five-years-after-its-initial-release-3844687">查佩尔·罗恩（Chappell Roan）邮报（Post Chappell Roan）获得了第一张英国首场单曲，即“粉红色小马俱乐部”（Pink Pony Club） - 首次发行五年后，</a>首次出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Chappell-Roan.-CREDIT_-Jeff-Kravitz_FilmMagic.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Chappell-Roan.-CREDIT_-Jeff-Kravitz_FilmMagic.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Chappell-Roan.-CREDIT_-Jeff-Kravitz_FilmMagic-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Chappell-Roan.-CREDIT_-Jeff-Kravitz_FilmMagic-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Chappell-Roan.-CREDIT_-Jeff-Kravitz_FilmMagic-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Chappell-Roan.-CREDIT_-Jeff-Kravitz_FilmMagic-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Chappell-Roan.-CREDIT_-Jeff-Kravitz_FilmMagic-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/chappell-roan">查佩尔·罗恩（Chappell Roan）</a>在首次发行五年后，获得了她的第一位英国第一单曲《粉红色小马俱乐部》（Pink Pony Club）。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多：<a href="https://www.nme.com/the-cover/chappell-roan-05-02-2024-3582467">查佩尔·罗恩（Chappell Roan）：流行超新星，他感觉就像是“拖拉赛”女孩之一</a></strong></li></ul><p>该曲目最初是在2020年通过大西洋唱片发行的，然后罗恩后来从唱片公司删除。在2023年，它被包括在她的首张专辑《 <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/chappell-roan-the-rise-and-fall-of-a-midwest-princess-review-debut-album-radar-3499595">中西部公主的崛起与堕落</a>》中，从那以后的几年中，它逐渐增长了崇拜。</p><p>现在，它终于在英国官方单打排行榜上以658,424英国的总销售额达到了令人垂涎的第一名。作为回应，Roan告诉<a href="https://www.officialcharts.com/chart-news/chappell-roan-pink-pony-club-number-1-uk/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>官方图表</em></a>：“从第一天开始，英国就一直在我身边，这真是令人难以置信的荣誉！！！”</p><p>去年八月， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/chappell-roan-achieves-first-uk-number-one-album-with-midwest-princess-almost-a-year-after-its-release-3782521">“中西部公主的兴衰”在其正式发行后一年就达到了专辑排行榜中的第一名</a>。这张专辑现已超过374,206英国的销售，并获得了铂金认证的正式认证。 </p><p><iframe title="Chappell Roan -Pink Pony Club（官方音乐视频）" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/GR3Liudev18?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>在发行时，罗恩（Roan）的首张专辑得到了<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/chappell-roan-the-rise-and-fall-of-a-midwest-princess-review-debut-album-radar-3499595"><i>NME</i>的发光四星级评论</a>，汉娜·迈尔里（Hannah Mylrea）将其描述为“毫不掩饰的有趣国歌”。</p><p>它读到：“敏锐的瞬间比一些薄弱的民谣更光明。” “然而，&#39;中西部公主的兴衰&#39;是Roan大胆而粗糙的笔的展示，在那里她将灼热的启示与一些美味的厚脸皮合唱一起放置。”</p><p>在其他Roan新闻中，她最近<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/chappell-roan-debuts-new-lesbian-anthem-country-song-on-snl-3809048">在去年11月在<em>星期六夜现场</em>露面时</a>首次表演了曲目后，最近一直在取笑她即将发行的单曲“ The Giver”。上个月，罗恩（Roan） <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/chappell-roan-reveals-plumber-version-of-new-single-the-giver-3841347">针对“送礼者”（The Giver）的两个变体宣布了乙烯基预订，称为“水管工版”和“律师版”</a> - 这些乙烯基订单预计将于8月发货。</p><p>该曲目将于3月13日发行， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/chappell-roan-details-upcoming-single-the-giver-my-take-on-cntry-3843643">本周早些时候，这首歌将是她的第一个祖国</a>。她在Instagram上写道：“我们从来没有做过乡村歌曲，我在乡村音乐中拥有如此特殊的位置。” “我每天早晨和下午在我的校车上听着它，并在Bon Fires，杂货店和卡拉OK酒吧在我周围旋转。” </p><figure id="attachment_3841348" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3841348" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3841348" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/chappell-roan@2000x1270-2.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/chappell-roan@2000x1270-2.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/chappell-roan@2000x1270-2-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/chappell-roan@2000x1270-2-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/chappell-roan@2000x1270-2-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/chappell-roan@2000x1270-2-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/chappell-roan@2000x1270-2-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3841348" class="wp-caption-text">查佩尔·罗恩（Chappell Roan）。学分：录音学院的丽贝卡·萨普/盖蒂图像</figcaption></figure><p>在去年7月的“送礼者”时，制片人丹·尼格罗（Dan Nigro）告诉<em><a href="https://www.nytimes.com/2024/10/21/arts/music/daniel-nigro-chappell-roan-olivia-rodrigo.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener">《纽约时报》（New York Times）</a></em> ，粉丝们可以期待一首有趣的，节奏的乡村歌曲”，其中有小提琴， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/chappell-roans-second-album-will-be-a-new-version-of-chappell-3805722">并将展示这位歌手的“新版本”</a> 。然后，正如<em><a href="https://uproxx.com/pop/chappell-roan-phone-number-the-giver/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Uproxx</a></em>所强调的那样，11月，流行歌星解释说，这首歌是一首受国家风格的单曲，回想起女性如何“完成工作”。</p><p>罗恩（Roan）的“送礼者”宣布是<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-chappell-roan-and-elton-john-perform-pink-pony-club-duet-at-oscars-viewing-party-3842978">在与埃尔顿·约翰（Elton John）在奥斯卡观看派对上与埃尔顿·约翰（Elton John）进行了“粉红色小马俱乐部”二重奏</a>之后不久。在埃尔顿·约翰（Elton John）的筹款活动中，她为一场完整的舞台上登台，其中包括约翰（John）的更多二重奏，“不要让太阳落在我身上”和“你的歌”和“你的歌”，她五年前在YouTube上介绍了这首歌，然后才找到主流名声。她还演唱了“曼哈顿裸体”，“超级图形超现代女孩”，“女性类诺农”，“热得很热”和“祝你好运，宝贝！”。</p><p>就在演出的前一天晚上，罗恩（Roan）用她的声音将她的<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/brit-awards">英国奖项</a>赢得了“ <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/chappell-roan-dedicates-her-brit-award-to-trans-artists-drag-queens-fashion-students-sex-workers-and-sinead-oconnor-3842755">跨跨艺术家，拖延皇后，拖到时尚的学生，性工作者和西纳·奥康纳（Sinead O&#39;Connor</a> ）”，然后<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/grammys-2025-chappell-roans-best-new-artist-acceptance-speech-demands-record-labels-treat-their-artists-as-valuable-employees-3833896">在第67届格莱美奖上使用她最佳的新艺术家演讲</a>之后成为头条新闻。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/chappell-roan-achieves-first-uk-number-one-single-with-pink-pony-club-five-years-after-its-initial-release-3844687">查佩尔·罗恩（Chappell Roan）邮报（Post Chappell Roan）获得了第一张英国首场单曲，即“粉红色小马俱乐部”（Pink Pony Club） - 首次发行五年后，</a>首次出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
