000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Celine-Dion.-CREDIT_-Kristina-Bumphrey_Variety-via-Getty-Images-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Celine-Dion.-CREDIT_-Kristina-Bumphrey_Variety-via-Getty-Images-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Celine-Dion.-CREDIT_-Kristina-Bumphrey_Variety-via-Getty-Images-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Celine-Dion.-CREDIT_-Kristina-Bumphrey_Variety-via-Getty-Images-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Celine-Dion.-CREDIT_-Kristina-Bumphrey_Variety-via-Getty-Images-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/celine-dion">席琳·迪翁（Celine Dion）</a>警告球迷不要在线流传的“假” <a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/ai">AI</a>生成的歌曲。</p><p>在昨天（3月7日）在Instagram上发表的一份声明中，歌手的代表写道：“引起我们的注意，未经批准的AI生成的音乐声称旨在包含Celine Dion的音乐表演，名称和相似性，目前正在网上和各种数字服务提供者中流通。”</p><p>它继续说：“请告知这些录音是假的，没有被批准，也不是她官方唱片的歌曲。”</p><p>尽管他们没有命名任何特定的歌曲，但AI生成的Dion封面演唱了福音歌曲“ Heal Me Lord”，最近被上传到YouTube，并积累了超过一百万的观看次数。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/DG50vb6x3O9/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; heigh